  <brief_summary>
    <textblock>
      Quality of life of patients with a history of drug allergy in Thailand will be studied.
    </textblock>
  </brief_summary>
  <detailed_description>
    <textblock>
      Thai patients with a history of drug allergy will be evaluated for their quality of life
      based on drug hypersensitivity quality of life questionnaire (DrHy-Q; Thai version) and The
      World Health Organization Quality of Life instrument (WHOQOL-BREF-THAI)
    </textblock>
  </detailed_description>
